4. Crystal Belvin-Scott

# Crystal Belvin-Scott

## Senior Administrative Program Coordinator Center Operations and Administration

Email: **[cscott@tacc.utexas.edu](mailto:cscott@tacc.utexas.edu)**

Crystal joined the TACC team on April 1, 2024 as the Senior Administrative Program Coordinator where she will be responsible for programmatic support of the administrative team and other duties that she is excited to learn. She come with almost 6 years of state service under her belt and 12 years in a leadership role. In her previous position at the Texas Department of State Health Services she was the 340B Program Coordinator and Team Lead where she was responsible for department operations, creating policies, stakeholder and user training and creating program resources in preparation for government proposal.

### Education

**Pharmacy Technician Program**  

Southern Careers Institute, 2006